item.title: CVE-2021-34655|2024-09-17T04:25:10.105Z -- wp%20songbook -- wp%20songbook
item.description: The WP Songbook WordPress plugin is vulnerable to Reflected Cross-Site Scripting via the url parameter found in the ~/inc/class.ajax.php file which allows attackers to inject arbitrary web scripts, in versions up to and including 2.0.11.
